      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link>https://one-ruri.github.io/posts/hello-world/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 17:41:53 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://one-ruri.github.io/posts/hello-world/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Welcome to &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/&#34;&gt;Hexo&lt;/a&gt;! This is your very first post. Check &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/docs/&#34;&gt;documentation&lt;/a&gt; for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html&#34;&gt;troubleshooting&lt;/a&gt; or you can ask me on &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;quick-start&#34;&gt;Quick Start&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-new-post&#34;&gt;Create a new post&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ hexo new &lt;span style=&#34;color:#d14&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;My New Post&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;More info: &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html&#34;&gt;Writing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;run-server&#34;&gt;Run server&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ hexo server&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;More info: &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/docs/server.html&#34;&gt;Server&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;generate-static-files&#34;&gt;Generate static files&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ hexo generate&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;More info: &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html&#34;&gt;Generating&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;deploy-to-remote-sites&#34;&gt;Deploy to remote sites&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ hexo deploy&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;More info: &lt;a href=&#34;https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html&#34;&gt;Deployment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
